289
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:34,760
Xiaoguang!

290
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,000
Stay with us. Don't faint.

291
00:21:38,560 --> 00:21:39,480
Xiaoguang!

292
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:42,200
We're getting you to the hospital soon!

293
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:42,920
Stay awake!

294
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,680
Go keep an eye on Liang Jiaju.

295
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,080
Get someone to take him away.

296
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:49,560
I'll take Xiaoguang to the hospital.

297
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,200
Can you do it by yourself?

298
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:53,120
How far have we come?

299
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:55,840
About two kilometers.

300
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,600
Alright, I'll carry him.

301
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:10,080
Be careful!

302
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:14,960
Captain Wang,

303
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,640
