304
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:32,320
Bei,

305
00:22:34,280 --> 00:22:36,120
I have something to tell you.

306
00:22:38,520 --> 00:22:39,720
It's about you and Nan, right?

307
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:41,280
Don't worry.

308
00:22:42,280 --> 00:22:43,480
I'll get everything taken care of
when we get back.

309
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,280
Just hang in there!

310
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:46,800
