311
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:51,160
Yao has a boyfriend now.

312
00:22:53,360 --> 00:22:55,200
It's Wu Gang.

313
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:58,600
Stop worrying
about other people's business.

314
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,400
Focus on yourself!

315
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,240
You'd better not

316
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,680
tell her I told you.

317
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:09,960
If you stay awake, I won't say a word.

318
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,520
Xiaoguang!

319
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,120
Come on, Uncle.

320
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:51,560
You guys go ahead.

321
00:23:51,560 --> 00:23:52,800
Head back to the station
once you're done.

322
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:54,560
I'll cook something for you all.

323
00:23:55,080 --> 00:23:55,880
Alright.

324
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,160
Xiaoguang.

325
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:56,640
Xiaoguang, leave.

326
00:24:57,560 --> 00:24:58,360
Xiaoguang!

327
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:00,520
Xiaoguang!

328
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,240
Run, Xiaoguang!

329
00:25:06,560 --> 00:25:07,760
Stay back!

330
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:14,840
Stay back!

331
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:18,320
Bei!

332
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:20,320
Stay back!

333
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:21,940
- Bei!
- Stay away from me!

334
00:25:21,940 --> 00:25:23,080
- Stay back!
- Zheng Bei!

335
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:36,460
- Bei!
- Zheng Bei!

336
00:25:36,460 --> 00:25:37,640
- Bei!
- Zheng Bei!

337
00:25:38,280 --> 00:25:40,120
- Bei!
- Zheng Bei!

338
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:44,880
Bei!

339
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:46,640
Hurry, go pick up Gu Yiran!

340
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:49,560
- Bei!
- Zheng Bei!

341
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:20,320
You're awake.

342
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,040
Where's Xiaoguang?

343
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:23,760
Bei.

344
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,720
Where's Xiaoguang?

345
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:28,160
Bei, you can't get up!

346
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:30,880
Look at you.

347
00:26:33,760 --> 00:26:34,320
Bei,

348
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,400
Bei, you...

349
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:38,880
You shouldn't go there for now.

350
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:43,000
Is he still alive?

351
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:46,000
Yes.

352
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:49,440
But the doctor said

353
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:54,640
he might not be able to wake up.

354
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,000
Bei.

355
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:27,960
Zheng Bei.

356
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:28,760
Bei.

357
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:31,400
Where's Xiaoguang?

358
00:27:33,040 --> 00:27:34,160
He's inside.

359
00:27:35,760 --> 00:27:36,960
Calm down.

360
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:41,200
I'm fine.

361
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,000
I just want to see him.

362
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:44,280
Bei...

363
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:45,240
Zheng Bei.

364
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:45,960
- You're still not fully recovered.
- Bei...

365
00:27:46,080 --> 00:27:47,240
It's okay. I'll just take a look.

366
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:48,800
Enough.

367
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:49,400
Zheng Bei.

368
00:27:50,040 --> 00:27:50,600
Director Gao.

369
00:27:50,800 --> 00:27:51,560
Director Gao.

370
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:53,720
You're injured.

371
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:55,120
You need to rest.

372
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,400
Go back to your room.

373
00:27:58,320 --> 00:27:59,640
Xiaoguang's made it through,

374
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:01,360
but he's still resting.

375
00:28:03,080 --> 00:28:04,200
You should rest, too.

376
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:09,440
I'm fine.

377
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:12,600
I was the one who brought him

378
00:28:13,600 --> 00:28:14,480
on the mission.

379
00:28:16,560 --> 00:28:18,200
I have to make sure he gets back safely.

380
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:27,200
Just let me see him for a moment.

381
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:34,000
He just got out of critical condition.

382
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:38,200
He suffered
from severe oxygen deprivation

383
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:39,760
and excessive blood loss.

384
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:43,680
Even the doctors
don't know when he'll wake up.

385
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:38,160
Nan.

386
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,760
Bei, you're awake.

387
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:45,440
Are you feeling better?

388
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:47,920
I'm fine.

389
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:51,000
I'm here to check on Xiaoguang.

390
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,160
Bei, speak up.

391
00:29:57,840 --> 00:29:58,920
Xiaoguang can hear you.

392
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,520
The doctor said

393
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,840
we should talk to him more.

394
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:07,360
Familiar voices are more likely
to get his attention.

395
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:08,960
Right, Xiaoguang?

396
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:37,000
Come on, you guys, talk to him.

397
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:55,960
Talk to him!

398
00:30:58,520 --> 00:31:01,160
You... He likes you the best.

399
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:05,160
Please, talk to him.

400
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:08,280
You taught him that song,
and he sings it so...

401
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:09,920
So well.

402
00:31:28,760 --> 00:31:30,160
I solemnly decided

403
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:33,080
to give my good luck to Ran.

404
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:57,800
Xiaoguang,

405
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,680
I'll teach you a new song tomorrow.

406
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:07,560
It's really good,

407
00:32:11,560 --> 00:32:13,080
but with your Cantonese,

408
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:16,200
it might be a bit difficult.

409
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:21,080
But I believe in you.

410
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:24,920
"Where there's a will,

411
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:27,560
there's a way."

412
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,600
Good thing you're just
teaching him a Cantonese song.

413
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:43,000
If you gave him a chemistry lesson,

414
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:44,680
we'd all doze off.

415
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:47,880
A chemistry lesson would be even better.

416
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:51,720
It'd wake him up for sure.

417
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,200
Xiaoguang,

418
00:32:53,720 --> 00:32:56,000
though Ran's not
giving you a chemistry lesson,

419
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:58,320
I'm coming here every day
to recite chemical formulas to you.

420
00:32:59,080 --> 00:32:59,960
It's alright. Don't worry.

421
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,480
Xiaoguang's a tough kid.

422
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:03,800
Starting tomorrow,

423
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:05,640
I'll come by every day
to give him a good scolding.

424
00:33:06,040 --> 00:33:07,640
He'll wake up in two days.

425
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:08,360
Don't cry.

426
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,400
You can't do that.

427
00:33:10,240 --> 00:33:12,800
You'll scare Xiaoguang even more.

428
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,920
Stop making Nan more worried.

429
00:33:15,120 --> 00:33:15,920
Nan, why don't you

430
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,920
sing Xiaoguang a song?

431
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:21,480
Just sing "Mother in the Candlelight".

432
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,120
It's no secret.

433
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:24,360
We all know about it, right?

434
00:33:29,080 --> 00:33:30,920
I've already informed
Xiaoguang's parents.

435
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:34,280
They'll be back tomorrow.

436
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:37,440
We'll take care

437
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:40,280
of all Xiaoguang's treatments.

438
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:53,560
Xiaoguang,

439
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:56,120
we're all here.

440
00:34:02,320 --> 00:34:03,400
And the bad guys have all been caught.

441
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:05,480
Don't worry.

442
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:08,720
It was all thanks to you today.

443
00:34:09,720 --> 00:34:10,440
Without you,

444
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:12,280
we wouldn't have completed the mission.

445
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:16,200
Xiaoguang, you did great.

446
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,400
I'm heading back
to interrogate them now.

447
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:25,600
You get some good rest here.

448
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:32,920
Alright,

449
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:34,800
that's it for now.

450
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:37,120
I'm off.

